{"tid":2044212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實x周年，xxx紀念日係咪應該轉下玩法","createTime":"2020-05-31T03:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T03:33:03.000Z","uid":195047,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fa862277c16c1c15df8f755833fce49fada3a62e","tid":2044212,"uid":195047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:27:08.000Z","msg":"代frd開po<br />\n大學都知運動已經持續左就快一年<br />\n唔同嘅「一周年」活動一定會有<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">612 721 811 831每月嘅8號同31</span></span>等<br />\n都會喺一年前嘅地方又嚟一次集結<br />\n我地知嘅班狗唔會唔知 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">等同預約自己人會出現喺果度</span><br />\n咁樣等同話比佢地聽我地喺幾時幾分一定會出現<br />\n大大增加佢地佈防同預備嘅時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係話呢啲紀念日子就係送頭，唔出得呢啲on9野<br />\n而係應該多返啲<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">無法預測，即興，臨時</span></span>嘅活動（如果如足夠嘅流動性）<br />\n歡迎下面討論"},{"pid":"8ad77579e09ced0a91e2243e338646da76f89bdf","tid":2044212,"uid":195047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:27:27.000Z","msg":"想知大家點諗"},{"pid":"c6fac902c18fb40b85fc1ce7c58fdb12f7946323","tid":2044212,"uid":195047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:27:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"716e83bd9c06bf4860eb3187a1b74775b7fb5ca4","tid":2044212,"uid":195047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:27:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fee4af965a3ff5742a9ab7b59d423dddefecdbd2","tid":2044212,"uid":195047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:28:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"080ba2dd476a7b7fba71253eba898b223dbd5fe9","tid":2044212,"uid":195047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:28:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16d7e1bd7fd1010d73a1130062dbb9fd70efe14c","tid":2044212,"uid":195047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:28:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5ce800d35128b2b755de3851899a855aca7f4e6","tid":204